data.description: Welcome to 3550 Carter Drive, Unit 11. This lovely condo, built in 1979, offers a direct entry like a townhouse, split-level open floor plan with 877 sq. ft. Highlights include two-bedrooms, one-and-one-half-bathrooms, soaring ceilings and a Nest thermostat. In unit washer and dryer, Laminate wood flooring flows throughout the unit. The living room includes a cozy gas fireplace. A Milgard slider opens to the patio with beautiful mountain vistas. Parking and storage are available in the detached, one-car garage. Close proximity to Skyline College and highly-rated schools. Explore nearby Westborough Square, Seafood City, Westborough Park, Serramonte mall, Costco, Trader Joe's, restaurants, coffee shops and grocery stores. Commuting is a breeze with BART, Caltrain and easy access to Highways 280 and 101. Enjoy a convenient location just minutes to San Francisco and South San Francisco's biotech companies.
